"4.  Height (m): " + $F{height} + "  Weight (kg): " + $F{weight} + "  Blood Type: " + $F{bloodType} + "\n" +
"5.  GSIS ID No.: " + $F{gsisId} + "\n" +
"6.  PAG-IBIG ID No.: " + $F{pagibigId} + "\n" +
